des:
Morning Tweet Tweet: Relaxing Sounds
Morning Tweet Tweet is a soothing sound. It's the right sound when you need a special atmosphere. It's going to help you concentrate, read, function, sleep or relax. 
How to use "Morning Tweet Tweet: Relaxing Sounds"?

You can say:
- "Alexa, open Morning Tweet Tweet"
- "Alexa, start Morning Tweet Tweet"
- "Alexa, play Morning Tweet Tweet"

It will automatically play the sound indefinitely until you say "Alexa, stop".
